ğŸ”¹ Examples:
Directive	           Use
*ngIf	        Show/hide elements conditionally
*ngFor	        Loop through items in a list
*ngSwitch	    Conditional switching



3ï¸âƒ£ Attribute Directive
ğŸ¨ These directives change the appearance or behavior of an element.
